According to Dr. Syzygium aromaticum's real time data, as of 20:00 Feb. 28, there were 39,859 confirmed cases, 78,926 confirmed cases, and 2,308 suspected cases. There were 7952 severe cases, 2791 deaths and 36312 cured cases.

As of February 27, the World Health Organization reported 3,664 confirmed cases outside China, an increase of 746 cases from the previous day.
